Read AGENTS.md first and follow it strictly.

Build one feature at a time. One screen. One integration.
Never multiple features in one prompt.

Constraint library:
- Do not change the screen design.
- Preserve the existing UI exactly.
- Do not expose any secrets in the client app.
- Do not introduce new libraries without asking.
- Do not modify files outside the requested folder.
- Do not refactor existing code.
- Do not add features that were not requested.
- Do not change existing navigation structure.

The game engine is server-authoritative. Client engine is for UI feedback only.
Never trust client-side game state for financial outcomes.
